.mdl-grid
	.mdl-cell.mdl-cell--12-col
	%h2 上架哪種商品？

.mdl-grid
	.mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp.mdl-cell.mdl-cell--3-col
		.mdl-card__title.mdl-card--expand{:style => "height:200px; background: rgba(199, 224, 172, 1) url('img/newproduct/in_transit.png') center 40px no-repeat; background-size: 85px;"}
			%a.mdl-card__title-text 實體商品
		.mdl-card__supporting-text
			需寄送之商品，支援各式運費與購物車機制。

	.mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp.mdl-cell.mdl-cell--3-col
		.mdl-card__title.mdl-card--expand{:style => "height:200px; background: rgba(237, 255, 251, 1) url('img/newproduct/download_2.png') center 40px no-repeat; background-size: 85px;"}
			%a.mdl-card__title-text 虛擬商品
		.mdl-card__supporting-text
			透過 Email 出貨之虛擬商品或服務。

	.mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp.mdl-cell.mdl-cell--3-col
		.mdl-card__title.mdl-card--expand{:style => "height:200px; background: rgba(255, 227, 248, 1) url('img/newproduct/google_logo.png') center 40px no-repeat; background-size: 85px;"}
			%a.mdl-card__title-text G單幫手
		.mdl-card__supporting-text
			使用 Google 表單收單，批次傳訊息與收款。

	.mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp.mdl-cell.mdl-cell--3-col
		.mdl-card__title.mdl-card--expand{:style => "height:200px; background: rgba(230, 229, 211, 1)url('img/newproduct/donate.png') center 40px no-repeat; background-size: 85px;"}
			%a.mdl-card__title-text 手打支持
		.mdl-card__supporting-text
			定期定額金流，訂閱、贊助、支持等等。

	.mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp.mdl-cell.mdl-cell--8-col.mdl-cell--2-offset
		.mdl-card__supporting-text.mdl-card--border_bottom
			%i.material-icons.with-text> build
			商品型態
		.card-padding
			.section
				%label.mdl-radio.mdl-js-radio.mdl-js-ripple-effect{for: "option-1"}
					%input#option-1.mdl-radio__button{name: "options", type: "radio", value: "2"}/
					%span.mdl-radio__label 實體商品
					%small 需寄送之商品
			.section
				%label.mdl-radio.mdl-js-radio.mdl-js-ripple-effect{for: "option-2"}
					%input#option-2.mdl-radio__button{name: "options", type: "radio", value: "2"}/
					%span.mdl-radio__label 數位商品（或服務）
					%small 透過 Email 出貨或是不需寄送之商品
			.section
				%label.mdl-radio.mdl-js-radio.mdl-js-ripple-effect{for: "option-3"}
					%input#option-3.mdl-radio__button{name: "options", type: "radio", value: "2"}/
					%span.mdl-radio__label 手打加一（適合團購、預購、登記...等）
					%small 使用 Google 表單收單，批次傳訊息與收款。
			.section
				%label.mdl-radio.mdl-js-radio.mdl-js-ripple-effect{for: "option-4"}
					%input#option-4.mdl-radio__button{name: "options", type: "radio", value: "2"}/
					%span.mdl-radio__label 手打支持
					%small 定期定額收費，批次傳訊息、批次收款。